    <div class="mt-16 sm:mt-32 px-4 sm:px-16 lg:px-24 mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100 sm:text-5xl">
        Software developer and outdoor enthusiast
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        Hey ðŸ‘‹,<br />
        my name is Thomas and I'm a software developer currently working with a great team at
        <a class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-500" href="https://www.zeiss.com/corporate/int/home.html"> @ZEISS</a>
        in Munich / Germany. <br />
        I'm professional at making stuff using .NET, Node.js, React and Next.js. I'm fluent in TypeScript / JS and C# and
        I love to try out new languages and technologies, especially in the field of functional programming. I'm a huge fan
        of
        <a class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-500" href="https://elixir-lang.org/">elixir</a> / erlang and
        <a class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-500" href="https://fsharp.org/"> F#</a> as well as
        <a
          class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-500"
          href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/apps/aspnet/web-apps/blazor"
